Scholarships and Financial Aid with Qadri International
Financial aid and scholarships are available for eligible students who choose to study in Latvia. Qadri International can provide information on the various scholarships and financial aid options available, as well as assist you in applying for them. Don't let finances be a barrier to your education – study in Latvia with Qadri International and unlock your potential!

Student Life in Latvia
Life as a student in Latvia is vibrant and exciting. You'll have the opportunity to meet students from all over the world, participate in various clubs and activities, and explore the country's rich cultural heritage. Whether you're studying in Riga, Daugavpils, or Liepaja, you'll find that there is never a dull moment in Latvia.

